{"tid":1465092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對付緊個極權政府，點解會有咁多人想急於求成？","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:43:52.000Z","uid":25833,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"a7ee809cc7d4bc3ce777f773e5d63ed915164fd7","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"好多人話2個月以黎，遊行無用，和理非無用<br />\n<br />\n民意無用，底線無用，外國人支持無用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係你地究竟係咪天真到，覺得所有野做一做就會即刻見效？唔係就唔想再做？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地究竟係出黎抗爭，定出黎食民主快餐？<br />\n<br />\n今日互屌左成日，名義上，阻到機場，實際上佢退左1步，我地自損3千<br />\n<br />\n究竟要打沉自己人氣勢到幾時先夠？我地行左幾個月，對於中共黎講，先岩岩開始出手，咁快就想玩完？你地究竟個決心有幾低？<br />\n<br />\n今日機場既事，無論點都好，阻已經成功左<br />\n<br />\n但光環無疑係比左政府戴<br />\n<br />\n希望大家未來可以諗一諗，對準政權<br />\n我地要攬炒既，係香港政府，唔係抗爭者自炒<br />\n唔好再做無意義既損失，記住呢個係一個長期戰<br />\n打緊超地獄級關卡，唔好妄想幾個月爆機<br />\n繼續裝備好自己，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地一直向緊贏既方向前進，終有一日，香港都係屬於香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n8月18日見</span></span>"},{"pid":"bca33e651772e30ec6afa27a36c468afed51b393","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d302fe735aa6c3832eea8ba750ea226c5b41485","tid":1465092,"uid":299368,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"革命邊可能2個月就得&hellip;&hellip;大家明唔明白民意對以後好多野都好有用<br />\n唔係一時三刻出現嘅野，雨傘雖然失敗，但係雨傘嘅文宣到依家都有影響<br />\n一講民意就鬧民意撚&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"9fb38d8c615302b8f952475d6b5e1507e63ebb07","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0d302fe735aa6c3832eea8ba750ea226c5b41485","tid":1465092,"uid":299368,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"革命邊可能2個月就得&hellip;&hellip;大家明唔明白民意對以後好多野都好有用<br />\n唔係一時三刻出現嘅野，雨傘雖然失敗，但係雨傘嘅文宣到依家都有影響<br />\n一講民意就鬧民意撚&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"真係唔想大家咁心急，突然間要放棄哂所有野，做所謂既攬炒<br />\n<br />\n呢種攬炒對政府一d用都無"},{"pid":"49dac06fd27ab2debdfb2fe536eb24003bbafaa0","tid":1465092,"uid":299368,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9fb38d8c615302b8f952475d6b5e1507e63ebb07","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0d302fe735aa6c3832eea8ba750ea226c5b41485","tid":1465092,"uid":299368,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"革命邊可能2個月就得&hellip;&hellip;大家明唔明白民意對以後好多野都好有用<br />\n唔係一時三刻出現嘅野，雨傘雖然失敗，但係雨傘嘅文宣到依家都有影響<br />\n一講民意就鬧民意撚&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"真係唔想大家咁心急，突然間要放棄哂所有野，做所謂既攬炒<br />\n<br />\n呢種攬炒對政府一d用都無"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:09:00.000Z","msg":"其實我睇好多評論都話，開始要從長計議，慢慢行&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n爭取普選08年就開始，可以睇得出任何野要時間，要滲透力，要長久嘅影響力，長遠一啲睇野，唔好注重面前短暫嘅成功&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但係連登同telegram普遍俾我嘅感覺好著急，覺得依幾個月成功唔到就唔得&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n但係睇返歷史，好多革命經過好耐嘅planning"},{"pid":"63f6e779f1e4afd90f9eccdc42ea60287d034f1d","tid":1465092,"uid":25514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"係咪因為覺得只有人數先係致勝關鍵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間一長d人又會投入返日常生活唔再出黎咁"},{"pid":"276c67f052abb64551748730f89cca71f4c10b9e","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:38:46.000Z","msg":"而加情況開始唔樂觀<br />\n<br />\n真心要停一停，諗一諗<br />\n<br />\n報導相信聽日會係一面倒"},{"pid":"1fa07430f223212f9932c5743222056bd2613d0b","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2487eb6f76d2132d74c1fefe6fb734838862752","tid":1465092,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471/tumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6c057950ed65cc1fac07eb212cfe3471%2Ftumblr_nfv4w34Uby1qcbtvqo5_250.gif&h=74060c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我地係唔需要洗佢地腦，甚至唔需要接觸任何人，要做既野只需要貼去多大陸人既地方都係廣獨／粵獨poster就得....<br />\n只要將廣獨思想文宣貼到通街都係，中共知道左就自然唔敢放自由行落黎<br />\n將廣獨思想輸出從而增加中共管治成本同時減少自由行黎香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR&d=3XxoN59xZ6GKXDea4epuE3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=48992d3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvBhkhWvLzeCzeR</a>"},{"pid":"816f02e3e54c5a46f8cba30bd7659a6b19817f70","tid":1465092,"uid":261330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:02:56.000Z","msg":"其實會做錯係好正常，當經驗，唔洗即刻割蓆"},{"pid":"02fafc2c7e21f98b8413c5c1cc4acd0eba4e7ffb","tid":1465092,"uid":142223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"個期限係中美貿易戰期間<br />\nTrump任期仲有一年半，唔係真係可以拖咁長"},{"pid":"2a0b233270278a3d1627571375c114e1c031c9e4","tid":1465092,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求下大家聽下陳雲既指點<br />\n倪匡 陳雲對共產黨同大勢既理解係好有啟發性<br />\n<br />\n大家要冷靜應對<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oe6cYHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOe6cYHJ.jpg&h=fb7b2ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPN0n9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPN0n9p.png&h=a2f35af5&s={SIZE}\"