":"2019-08-14T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"因為大家都怕步雨革後塵<br />\n而且今次輸 就真係唔洗諗下次"},{"pid":"8f6e6b5abb61aa158296dfb59f86f82f70cfb927","tid":1465092,"uid":107686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"818見"},{"pid":"dac05d139a74001c4eac5c6a1781e50e469f87b4","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a0b233270278a3d1627571375c114e1c031c9e4","tid":1465092,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求下大家聽下陳雲既指點<br />\n倪匡 陳雲對共產黨同大勢既理解係好有啟發性<br />\n<br />\n大家要冷靜應對<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oe6cYHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOe6cYHJ.jpg&h=fb7b2ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPN0n9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPN0n9p.png&h=a2f35af5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLkJkV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLkJkV5.png&h=ba8955b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMCzsA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMCzsA5.jpg&h=1b96d916&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"倪匡其實都真係好有智慧，唔聽連登仔講都聽下佢地講<br />\n<br />\n人地真真正正受中共既壓逼，恨不得中共快d死，都無我地咁心急，都能夠睇清局勢，點解我地呢代咁有智慧咁有理想，會諗唔到？"},{"pid":"55701f772852ade217f73d20f002b6fc82a8568c","tid":1465092,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"呢排明顯大家心急左<br />\n理解到 但要提一下要冷靜<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n有冇計可以減少&ldquo;勇武&rdquo; &ldquo;和理非&rdquo;呢啲標籤黎指代人<br />\n大家都係手足，成日呢啲形容行為嘅字眼去指代群體好易起分化作用<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<br />\n<br />\n請不要說推，說<br />\n721 811<br />\n818我會上街<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔做捉鬼敢死隊"},{"pid":"ae9ad711e32ecc38e334036f3fbe9d7c465082cf","tid":1465092,"uid":120760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"用開快車做比喻<br />\n大家知道剎車係要剎到才叫有用<br />\n<br />\n和理非就係果個剎車制, 見到要轉彎就要剎定部車等部車可以安全過彎<br />\n但勇武就話剎乜鬼剎？仲有足夠距離，到最後一刻才踩，你咁早踩做乜？屌你老母鬼<br />\n<br />\n和理非問勇武部車唔踩剎車要點樣先可以成功過彎<br />\n勇武回答：飄移過彎lor, 你唔好好控住個剎車力度我點過彎呀?<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都想快少少到終點, 不過方式唔同<br />\n條路難行大家都知, 真係只能希望不再割蓆"},{"pid":"a92e72b90c86134d2f6de617800851af9bc43053","tid":1465092,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>8月18和理非日</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af215b13f36ddf5aa288a5f53c2bc10393077967","tid":1465092,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bca33e651772e30ec6afa27a36c468afed51b393","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"關於機場禁制令反思<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3db5a3bf5ee9abd0fa954438e95ffeb6a5e8e32","tid":1465092,"uid":264121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:34.000Z","msg":"賭魔&lt;陳金城&gt;有野想同年輕人講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469594\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469594</a>"},{"pid":"c8dd1adb459261926b50170c3422e1453078fac2","tid":1465092,"uid":290973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d302fe735aa6c3832eea8ba750ea226c5b41485","tid":1465092,"uid":299368,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"革命邊可能2個月就得&hellip;&hellip;大家明唔明白民意對以後好多野都好有用<br />\n唔係一時三刻出現嘅野，雨傘雖然失敗，但係雨傘嘅文宣到依家都有影響<br />\n一講民意就鬧民意撚&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:21:41.000Z","msg":"關於機場禁制令反思<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1469410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1469410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6500942301d417bb9975f2456f6db9e487e1e06e","tid":1465092,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac05d139a74001c4eac5c6a1781e50e469f87b4","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a0b233270278a3d1627571375c114e1c031c9e4","tid":1465092,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求下大家聽下陳雲既指點<br />\n倪匡 陳雲對共產黨同大勢既理解係好有啟發性<br />\n<br />\n大家要冷靜應對<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oe6cYHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOe6cYHJ.jpg&h=fb7b2ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPN0n9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPN0n9p.png&h=a2f35af5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLkJkV5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLkJkV5.png&h=ba8955b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MMCzsA5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMMCzsA5.jpg&h=1b96d916&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:18:27.000Z","msg":"倪匡其實都真係好有智慧，唔聽連登仔講都聽下佢地講<br />\n<br />\n人地真真正正受中共既壓逼，恨不得中共快d死，都無我地咁心急，都能夠睇清局勢，點解我地呢代咁有智慧咁有理想，會諗唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:24:37.000Z","msg":"Exactly<br />\n人地曾經被共匪壓<br />\n都知所進退<br />\n<br />\n大家要睇下2位既文"},{"pid":"b48191c5d4249e54560be795e0db867d8f432161","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59da210901229c1a9159386ce4c67c9b19c46a7d","tid":1465092,"uid":142223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"要對抗極權政府唔係講緊話搞幾多年就可以成功<br />\n而係要有特殊嘅事件，天時地利人和下先可以成功，而家就係唯一機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"我地成功把握左咁多個機會，唔認同你話呢個係唯一機會<br />\n<br />\n我都唔認為而加你搞到機場，林鄭會即刻跪低<br />\n<br />\n唔好再幻想得咁美好，老實講，破壞野係最舒服既抗爭方法，一了百了唔洗煩<br />\n<br />\n但咁係有效既，就一早做左，大家都心知肚明，要成功一定係最辛苦既方法，一步一步話比極權政府聽，人民係從來唔會向極權退縮<br />\n而唔係衝埋去同你死過，然後爆炸炸死自己"},{"pid":"2b8ad388035d8fbccdde1691a9510660d70778a4","tid":1465092,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7ee809cc7d4bc3ce777f773e5d63ed915164fd7","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:33.000Z","msg":"好多人話2個月以黎，遊行無用，和理非無用<br />\n<br />\n民意無用，底線無用，外國人支持無用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係你地究竟係咪天真到，覺得所有野做一做就會即刻見效？唔係就唔想再做？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地究竟係出黎抗爭，定出黎食民主快餐？<br />\n<br />\n今日互屌左成日，名義上，阻到機場，實際上佢退左1步，我地自損3千<br />\n<br />\n究竟要打沉自己人氣勢到幾時先夠？我地行左幾個月，對於中共黎講，先岩岩開始出手，咁快就想玩完？你地究竟個決心有幾低？<br />\n<br />\n今日機場既事，無論點都好，阻已經成功左<br />\n<br />\n但光環無疑係比左政府戴<br />\n<br />\n希望大家未來可以諗一諗，對準政權<br />\n我地要攬炒既，係香港政府，唔係抗爭者自炒<br />\n唔好再做無意義既損失，記住呢個係一個長期戰<br />\n打緊超地獄級關卡，唔好妄想幾個月爆機<br />\n繼續裝備好自己，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地一直向緊贏既方向前進，終有一日，香港都係屬於香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n8月18日見</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"無錯要重整旗鼓"},{"pid":"739ac7651746fdee84055558ae90935cd2b20274","tid":1465092,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5d289c5dfe8cd43bb578aa7f875559a0a098c38","tid":1465092,"uid":86869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"因為大家都怕步雨革後塵<br />\n而且今次輸 就真係唔洗諗下次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:25:59.000Z","msg":"就係輸就無下次 就更加應該從長計議"},{"pid":"d32d23605ac832901fbd5b074764becc26580b3f","tid":1465092,"uid":142223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b48191c5d4249e54560be795e0db867d8f432161","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"59da210901229c1a9159386ce4c67c9b19c46a7d","tid":1465092,"uid":142223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"要對抗極權政府唔係講緊話搞幾多年就可以成功<br />\n而係要有特殊嘅事件，天時地利人和下先可以成功，而家就係唯一機會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"我地成功把握左咁多個機會，唔認同你話呢個係唯一機會<br />\n<br />\n我都唔認為而加你搞到機場，林鄭會即刻跪低<br />\n<br />\n唔好再幻想得咁美好，老實講，破壞野係最舒服既抗爭方法，一了百了唔洗煩<br />\n<br />\n但咁係有效既，就一早做左，大家都心知肚明，要成功一定係最辛苦既方法，一步一步話比極權政府聽，人民係從來唔會向極權退縮<br />\n而唔係衝埋去同你死過，然後爆炸炸死自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:28:57.000Z","msg":"我個唯一機會唔係指緊機場<br />\n係指緊成場運動<br />\n我係見到有人話爭取十幾年，從長計議先講呢啲野"},{"pid":"c01b7e9424dcc5419216fe364b284dec2fb71550","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aae31cbf74dc5276be81ec1de165e07ce489da5d","tid":1465092,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"民主快餐講得好 個個都以為一朝半夕搞得掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"要成功，一定係慢慢煲慢慢煮<br />\n<br />\n呢個極權政府擺到明唔會受你套快攻硬闖影響，你仲要用更快硬更硬既方式撞埋去，所謂既「攬炒」方式，你估你撞死左自己，個政府死得未？<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係自己攬炒，唔係同個政府攬炒，個政府用錢就搭到出黎，香港同中共多多的就是錢，你有幾多條人命黎同佢鬥撞？"},{"pid":"f387d912394540a87e93772ea3ccc25c9974250f","tid":1465092,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de73164af0c96e4dcb138093514e8953357a180","tid":1465092,"uid":187241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"耐性!!!!!!!事成之後再算帳！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">PATiENT</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ffd8c84db4f14d0f31f0a23dd7f815a1fe6d209","tid":1465092,"uid":187241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfc11367a545cc24d6555b368fb1b837ea295580","tid":1465092,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"FREE HONG KONG DEMOCRACY NOW"},{"pid":"8f2a38e001823c25e0240c6cf752f409d93bd149","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5d289c5dfe8cd43bb578aa7f875559a0a098c38","tid":1465092,"uid":86869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:17:51.000Z","msg":"因為大家都怕步雨革後塵<br />\n而且今次輸 就真係唔洗諗下次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:34:46.000Z","msg":"我地其實已經比雨革更加成功<br />\n<br />\n無必要放棄哂呢2個月既成果，同人鬥撞<br />\n<br />\n老實講，2個月只係一個開端，岩岩過左第一關boss<br />\n<br />\n咁快頂唔順唔想玩，咁你要諗清楚自己適唔適合抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n勇武，係有勇有謀，以武制暴<br />\n而唔係衝埋去死"},{"pid":"50dacf81174322761052ea577b1222aab53afd62","tid":1465092,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"要令極權屈服， 一系用強佢一倍以上既武力，但大家知咁係無可能<br />\n一系人民既抗爭，但依樣係需要團結，有勇有謀，思想清晰， 仲要以月，年計持續既抗爭<br />\n<br />\n試想想極權唔可能咁易放棄手上既財權"},{"pid":"209859361aed49365fcebe17b7136381ca08c623","tid":1465092,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:35:18.000Z","msg":"捉到對家又唔想失威，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n手持「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類。<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"309b395e9bb103a380345f07dc5519d555ba7972","tid":1465092,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7eb839cb618120e32fb58e14b4c43d2b5005ae","tid":1465092,"uid":293308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n【緊急號召】教協遊行 呼籲老師支持罷課<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YN4BGd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYN4BGd8.jpg&h=294234f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d63f369b8c31e488b5f5d633c7f30149a56e3c3","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55701f772852ade217f73d20f002b6fc82a8568c","tid":1465092,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:04.000Z","msg":"呢排明顯大家心急左<br />\n理解到 但要提一下要冷靜<br />\n<br />\n----------<br />\n<br />\n有冇計可以減少&ldquo;勇武&rdquo; &ldquo;和理非&rdquo;呢啲標籤黎指代人<br />\n大家都係手足，成日呢啲形容行為嘅字眼去指代群體好易起分化作用<br />\n<br />\n試下說 勇武手法/和理非手法<br />\n任何手足都可以唔同場合，用唔同手法做事架<br />\n<br />\n請不要說推，說<br />\n721 811<br />\n818我會上街<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n唔做捉鬼敢死隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"岩，呢期越來越多標籤<br />\n<br />\n一邊又指責勇武，另一邊又話和理非分化割蓆<br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層，大家都係為件事好，真係割蓆仲會同你講道理？<br />\n<br />\n有心既大家都係勇武，大家都係和理非，一個人唔係得一個面<br />\n<br />\n林鄭呢d狗賊就係得陰險既一面，大家無理由同佢一樣"},{"pid":"36ee138ed0c34dc623da4e95d697b3c3234402c2","tid":1465092,"uid":294052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:03.000Z","msg":"我地係應該抱住敢攬炒既心去對抗極權 而唔係諗住同佢一齊死而去攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4191855b52a03826f42949fecbae50442dfe59","tid":1465092,"uid":25833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae9ad711e32ecc38e334036f3fbe9d7c465082cf","tid":1465092,"uid":120760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:19:22.000Z","msg":"用開快車做比喻<br />\n大家知道剎車係要剎到才叫有用<br />\n<br />\n和理非就係果個剎車制, 見到要轉彎就要剎定部車等部車可以安全過彎<br />\n但勇武就話剎乜鬼剎？仲有足夠距離，到最後一刻才踩，你咁早踩做乜？屌你老母鬼<br />\n<br />\n和理非問勇武部車唔踩剎車要點樣先可以成功過彎<br />\n勇武回答：飄移過彎lor, 你唔好好控住個剎車力度我點過彎呀?<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都想快少少到終點, 不過方式唔同<br />\n條路難行大家都知, 真係只能希望不再割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"好好既比喻<br />\n<br />\n大家都想過終點，只係唔想你終點到未到，架車又爛哂，條軚又磨蝕哂姐<br />\n<br />\n呢個比賽擺明就係馬拉松式，提提大家到終點前仲有好長既路要走，唔好覺得未見到終點，就等於輸<br />\n<br />\n明明已經跑到咁遠"},{"pid":"4a14aec746c9edb073ddef5c6725d963dbbed3d0","tid":1465092,"uid":230434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:44:34.000Z","msg":"三年計劃<br />\n「在治安方面，支持大灣區內地9市的區（縣）與香港、澳門片區、堂區建立結對交流機制。建立大灣區社會治安治理聯動機制，加強粵港澳警務合作交流